ctice.12-factor-app.processes","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":3,"offset":548},"end":{"line":13,"column":44,"offset":589},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"tech.practice.12-factor-app.processes"}},{"from":{"fname":"tech.practice.12-factor-app","id":"12-factor-app","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":4,"offset":1707},"end":{"line":29,"column":49,"offset":1752},"indent":[]},"value":"tech.practice.12-factor-app.disposability"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"12-factor-app","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"disposability\">Disposability<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#disposability\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Maximize robustness with fast startup and graceful shutdown</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/blog/notes/12fa-06-processes\">Processes</a> are dispoable.\n<ul>\n<li>Elastic scaling</li>\n<li>Rapid deployment of code or <a href=\"/blog/notes/12fa-03-configuration\">Configuration</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Minimise startup time.\n<ul>\n<li>Ready in second(s) from cold</li>\n<li>Easier to relocate</li>\n<li>Easier to use spot instances</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/blog/notes/12fa-06-processes\">Processes</a> shut down gracefully\n<ul>\n<li>Stop listening on the service <a href=\"/blog/notes/12fa-07-port-binding\">port</a></li>\n<li>Let current transactions complete (draining)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/blog/notes/12fa-06-processes\">Processes</a> should be robust against sudden death in case of hardware failure:\n<ul>\n<li>Queueing backend</li>\n<li>Return jobs to the queue on failure.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/blog/notes/12-factor-app\">12-Factor App</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Dustin Barnes","desc":"","updated":1681759798693,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained"